FBIS4-18146 "drweu062_q_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-062 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 TURKEY Ciller Refuses Resignation `Gesture' Ciller Refuses Resignation `Gesture' NC3103055794 Paris AFP in English 0230 GMT 31 Mar 94 NC3103055794 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Ankara, March 31 (AFP)--Four Turkish ministers symbolically handed their resignation to Prime Minister Tansu Ciller late Wednesday [31 March] after failing to win election as mayors in municipal elections Sunday, a government source said. In a statement, Ciller thanked the four, all members of her True Path Party, for their "gesture" but said she had no intention of reshuffling the cabinet at the moment.
